# Database Backups — <%= appName %>

MyCLI can create database backups using native tools for your configured engine (`<%= database %>`).

## Commands

```bash
my backup run              # Create a backup in ./backups
my backup run --dry-run    # Preview commands without executing
my backup list             # List existing backups
```

## Environment

Set `DATABASE_URL` in `.env` before running backups.

## Restore

Restore procedures depend on your database engine — consult your provider documentation and test restores regularly.
